title: Green Tourism silver award for Conference and Events (Keele University)
text: ( Source : Keele University ) Green Tourism silver award for Conference and Events Posted on 12 October 2015 Keele University Conference and Events has achieved silver status in the highly accredited Green Tourism Scheme at the first attempt -
